WEBVTT

00:03.181 --> 00:05.350
This stamp may be worth a lot of money.

00:08.218 --> 00:11.183
This is a glimpse of what the future may look like.

00:14.298 --> 00:16.299
It's possible you might have to go to court.

00:18.020 --> 00:21.099
I'm also worried I might not understand his accent.

00:24.428 --> 00:26.711
Maybe you could be a great writer.

00:28.851 --> 00:31.247
Maybe I'm getting old, as my friends would say.

00:34.629 --> 00:38.106
Perhaps we will, one day. Keep in touch, Mina.

00:40.358 --> 00:43.323
Perhaps they'll be the beginning of a new herd in this area.

00:47.649 --> 00:50.387
She will probably come to my house tomorrow.

00:52.255 --> 00:55.106
Good idea. There will probably be a lot of people there.

00:58.261 --> 01:00.714
Chances are, they're not telling you the truth.

